                <callout1 type="arabic">IPR Valve</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>The IPR valve can be removed (if required) before or after removing the high pressure oil pump.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <para>Use a 28 mm (1-1/8 in) deep socket to unscrew the IPR valve from the high pressure oil pump body.</para>
